headline: Trane CEO expands on the HVAC operator's stock boom, innovations
summary: HVAC company Trane Technologies (TT) stock has hit record highs in recent weeks, managing to outperform despite extended volatility. Trane Chairman and CEO Dave Regnery sits down with Julie Hyman to uncover the so-called "why behind the high," going in depth about his company's involvement in building out cooling systems for AI data centers and the developer's approach to innovation in other business verticals, such as residential spaces. To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Market Domination here.
